WEBVTT

1
00:01:40.520 --> 00:01:42.310
Deodorizer?

2
00:01:42.310 --> 00:01:44.770
Um, Yamada-san?

3
00:01:45.630 --> 00:01:47.020
Do I...

4
00:01:47.020 --> 00:01:51.300
Um, how do I put this?

5
00:01:52.800 --> 00:01:55.580
Actually, never mind.

6
00:01:58.000 --> 00:02:01.820
With the bag, your total 
comes to 1,563 yen.

7
00:02:02.540 --> 00:02:03.480
Right.

8
00:02:04.090 --> 00:02:07.620
It's not something I can ask 
someone who's on the clock.

9
00:02:10.750 --> 00:02:13.050
Here's your change and receipt.

10
00:02:14.170 --> 00:02:15.550
Thank you for shopping with us.

11
00:02:16.360 --> 00:02:17.490
Thank you.

12
00:02:23.790 --> 00:02:25.650
Shit workplace,

13
00:02:26.160 --> 00:02:27.960
shit boss.

14
00:02:28.710 --> 00:02:31.170
Now, deodorizer.

15
00:02:31.170 --> 00:02:33.070
And a question on the tip of his tongue.

16
00:02:38.500 --> 00:02:40.080
I think I've got it.

17
00:02:41.610 --> 00:02:43.080
Sasaki-san.

18
00:02:43.330 --> 00:02:45.330
Did somebody say you reeked of cigarettes?

19
00:02:48.210 --> 00:02:51.400
Are you a mind reader, Tayama-san?

20
00:02:53.070 --> 00:02:56.220
Compared to you, everybody else 
is somewhat of a mind reader.

21
00:02:57.570 --> 00:03:00.940
I just saw you picking up 
deodorizer in there.

22
00:03:01.800 --> 00:03:03.300
From where?

23
00:03:03.300 --> 00:03:05.600
Hey, it's not a lie.

24
00:03:08.100 --> 00:03:11.630
Anyway, you're right. 
My boss hates the concept of smoking.

25
00:03:11.630 --> 00:03:14.740
He yelled at me, saying, 
"You reek! Do something about it!"

26
00:03:14.740 --> 00:03:16.220
Wow, I hit the bull's-eye.

27
00:03:17.430 --> 00:03:20.340
Well, it's the fate of all 
smokers everywhere.

28
00:03:26.820 --> 00:03:30.690
If you brush your teeth after you smoke, 
you'll get rid of most of the stench.

29
00:03:32.040 --> 00:03:35.420
Then just spray your clothes, 
and you're good to go.

30
00:03:35.420 --> 00:03:37.300
But sometimes...

31
00:03:39.030 --> 00:03:42.250
you get the whiners 
like I did the other... day?

32
00:03:43.510 --> 00:03:45.760
You're incredible, Tayama-san!

33
00:03:45.760 --> 00:03:48.270
It's so cool that you know all this!

34
00:03:48.620 --> 00:03:52.280
Eh, I'm just passing on a senpai's advice.

35
00:03:55.440 --> 00:03:58.740
But you're the one who told me.

36
00:04:05.850 --> 00:04:07.910
Sasaki-san, shake.

37
00:04:07.910 --> 00:04:10.180
Huh? O-Okay?

38
00:04:10.670 --> 00:04:14.000
Wait, "shake"? Tayama-san?

39
00:04:15.590 --> 00:04:16.920
For you.

40
00:04:17.340 --> 00:04:19.770
It's the deodorizing mist I use.

41
00:04:21.610 --> 00:04:23.760
It looks expensive. Are you sure?

42
00:04:23.760 --> 00:04:26.760
No biggie. It's half-empty, 
and I have more at home.

43
00:04:27.380 --> 00:04:31.940
Thank you. This is so fancy.

44
00:04:32.360 --> 00:04:37.180
As long as you don't go overboard, 
nobody at work will notice the scent.

45
00:04:38.950 --> 00:04:40.490
Do you like how it smells?

46
00:04:41.460 --> 00:04:43.650
What scent is it?

47
00:04:43.650 --> 00:04:45.090
Wanna check?

48
00:04:47.020 --> 00:04:50.080
I usually spray it 
around here, so feel free.

49
00:04:52.380 --> 00:04:54.340
I'm not going to sniff you!

50
00:04:54.340 --> 00:04:58.590
Aw, I thought you'd go for it.

51
00:04:59.730 --> 00:05:04.090
Tayama-san, do you see me 
as a dog or something?

52
00:05:10.060 --> 00:05:12.100
A Labrador retriever, maybe?

53
00:05:12.100 --> 00:05:15.360
Huh? Wh-What's that?

54
00:05:15.360 --> 00:05:16.200
A dog breed.

55
00:05:16.200 --> 00:05:18.310
So I was right!

56
00:05:41.990 --> 00:05:44.630
Now I just spray this.

57
00:05:45.760 --> 00:05:51.020
Wait... She said not to go overboard, 
but how much is the normal amount?

58
00:05:51.390 --> 00:05:54.530
It's easy to tell with my 
usual deodorizing sprays.

59
00:05:55.940 --> 00:05:57.410
Wow, somebody's fashionable.

60
00:05:57.410 --> 00:05:58.650
Whoa! Suzuki?

61
00:06:00.560 --> 00:06:05.740
Telling us smokers we reek is basically 
the chief's way of saying good morning!

62
00:06:05.740 --> 00:06:07.950
Don't take it so seriously, man!

63
00:06:07.950 --> 00:06:10.660
But just think about it.

64
00:06:10.660 --> 00:06:15.180
Brush your teeth after you smoke 
and apply some of this mist,

65
00:06:15.180 --> 00:06:19.460
and voilà, you've got your scent care 
down pat, or so I've heard.

66
00:06:19.460 --> 00:06:21.710
Heard? From whom?

67
00:06:21.710 --> 00:06:24.310
Huh? Uh, well...

68
00:06:25.630 --> 00:06:27.970
Just you try introducing me.

69
00:06:29.710 --> 00:06:30.460
Take that.

70
00:06:30.850 --> 00:06:34.730
That's cold! What the hell was that for?!

71
00:06:34.730 --> 00:06:38.000
Wow, that smells great!

72
00:06:38.000 --> 00:06:39.860
If you go home smelling so good,

73
00:06:39.860 --> 00:06:42.780
your wife'll fall in love 
with you all over again!

74
00:06:44.090 --> 00:06:48.740
Don't be stupid. Keiko-chan's 
already head over heels for me.

75
00:06:49.540 --> 00:06:53.810
But I don't particularly mind 
if she moves up to the next stage of love!

76
00:06:56.530 --> 00:06:58.630
Tell me more, buddy.

77
00:06:58.630 --> 00:07:02.590
Like I said, brush your teeth 
and use a mist.

78
00:07:02.590 --> 00:07:04.010
Just like this.

79
00:07:08.740 --> 00:07:10.390
Welcome!

80
00:07:10.920 --> 00:07:13.020
Here's your change and receipt.

81
00:07:13.310 --> 00:07:14.950
Thank you.

82
00:07:15.550 --> 00:07:16.600
Huh?

83
00:07:17.020 --> 00:07:22.650
Sasaki-san, you kind of smell 
like Tayama-chan today.

84
00:07:24.150 --> 00:07:29.910
No! That's just because... 
Gah! I'm so embarrassed!

85
00:07:31.670 --> 00:07:33.870
Oh, I got this mist from her 
the other day,

86
00:07:33.870 --> 00:07:36.760
but I didn't get to ask her 
how much of it to use.

87
00:07:37.920 --> 00:07:40.260
I guess I used too much today.

88
00:07:45.620 --> 00:07:49.330
S-Sorry about that! Thank you!

89
00:07:52.720 --> 00:07:55.560
Yamada-chan, you can clock out.

90
00:07:57.050 --> 00:07:59.770
Are you okay? Did something happen?

91
00:07:59.770 --> 00:08:00.560
No...

92
00:08:01.330 --> 00:08:04.820
I just wanted to tease a little, but...

93
00:08:05.490 --> 00:08:09.150
That reaction actually made me blush, too.

94
00:09:21.150 --> 00:09:24.090
I owe Master Tayama big time.

95
00:09:27.710 --> 00:09:31.410
I hope she'll like my return gift.

96
00:09:36.530 --> 00:09:38.540
Tayama-san, good even...

97
00:09:38.540 --> 00:09:39.420
Huh?

98
00:09:40.890 --> 00:09:42.790
What?!

99
00:09:42.790 --> 00:09:47.040
A-A-A different employee?!
